Not quite.  We want to validate that the RI's equivalent of hasCheckedException() follows the MH chain thru the target of a Mutable or Volatile CallSite.
We already know - by spec - how all the CS operate when invoked.  It's the hasCheckedException() behaviour that's in question.
So something like:
